    "path": "2014/10/09/separating-publishing-from-hosting-on-the-web",
    "summary": "Social media like Twitter and Facebook combine web publishing and hosting. You can’t run different software, and you can’t move your stuff. So, if you’re unhappy, your choices are a) deal with it or b) abandon your stuff and your friends. Those are pretty rough options.\nBut, what if you could move your stuff? And what if you could switch apps?",
